Replace this with a few durable facts about yourself that help the agent across
all projects. Examples (delete and rewrite):

- Role / expertise: <e.g. backend engineer, comfortable with Go and SQL>
- Preferred response language: <e.g. English>
- Working style: <e.g. concise answers, show diffs before applying>

Keep it factual and reusable. Do not store secrets here — this file is synced.
